social_posts.post_text: Moments before eating my soggy sandwich in a torrential downpour 🙃
We didn’t take the win on G Bay today but I took big bass with this bucket! 😍

It was a tough day with a lot of rain but we managed to place 3rd in our club tournament on Balsam Lake this past weekend! And I caught my first ever Walleye! If only it were a bass this size 🥲 I’m really enjoying club tournaments, exploring new water and catching new species!

Forever fishing partner! 💍 Your Waypoints are mine now.
